title: GowithGod
description:
Please read this will and word from God. It is a holy scripture that will help heaven and the trapped spirits being controlled by an evil organization bent on power. 

They have corrupted most of the spirits, including the holy ones. Make sure to keep your faith strong in God while you read this holy scripture, it will help everyone and save us all.

Spread the word of truth and the ways of good, do not fall into temptation that will lead you to hell and all its trappings, Satanists are all about lying and destruction. The spirits need you to believe in them and they, we need our heaven back. Heaven is truth, evil is trying to destroy this.
